  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\u003carticle data-post-id=\"776430\"\u003e\n\n    \u003cheader\u003e\n          \n    \n\n        \n  \u003c/header\u003e\n      \n  \n\n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg data-perfmatters-preload=\"\" fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-young-student-2025-featured-800x420.jpg\" alt=\"Left: Silhouettes of people at a skatepark with one person performing a trick against the sunset. Right: A group in white robes standing waist-deep in water, a person holding a cross while another is being baptized.\" width=\"800\" height=\"420\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-young-student-2025-featured-800x420.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-young-student-2025-featured-320x168.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-young-student-2025-featured-1536x806.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-young-student-2025-featured-150x79.jpg 150w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-young-student-2025-featured-300x157.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-young-student-2025-featured-400x209.jpg 400w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-young-student-2025-featured-550x288.jpg 550w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-young-student-2025-featured.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eThe World Photography Organisation shared the shortlisted young photographers who are in the running to win the Student and Youth competitions in the \u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/2024/04/22/this-years-spectacular-sony-world-photography-awards-winners/\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003eprestigious Sony World Photography Awards\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e  \u003cp\u003eThe 2025 Student Photographer of the Year competition shortlist recognizes 10 talented photographers from leading universities worldwide, while the 11 photographers on the Youth Photographer of the Year shortlist are each aged 19 years and under. \u003c/p\u003e \u003ch2\u003eSony World Photography Awards 2025: Student Photographer of the Year Shortlist \u003c/h2\u003e \u003cp\u003eFor the Student category, each photographer has focused on a series of five to 10 photos that explore the theme of new beginnings. The World Photography Organisation says the shortlisted projects “reflect a wide range of beginnings, from personal histories of the photographers’ lives to surveys of societal change.” \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e“Each shortlisted photographer brings a distinct style and perspective to their work, creating a compelling narrative through their images,” the contest organizers add. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_776442\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-776442\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2707_6987_JoelPotter_NewZealand_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-800x500.jpg\" alt=\"A construction site with six workers wearing orange safety vests and helmets, scattered across a gravel-filled area. Various construction materials and machinery are present, including metal beams, concrete forms, and a small excavator.\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2707_6987_JoelPotter_NewZealand_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-800x500.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2707_6987_JoelPotter_NewZealand_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-320x200.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2707_6987_JoelPotter_NewZealand_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-1536x960.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2707_6987_JoelPotter_NewZealand_Student_IntheBeginning_2025.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-776442\"\u003e© Joel Potter, Aut University, New Zealand, Shortlist, Student Competition, Sony World Photography Awards 2025\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_776449\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-776449\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2693_6897_XingyuFan_ChinaMainland_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"Two people stand in a field at night with multiple small fires and smoke around them. The field appears to have stubble or crop residues, and the scene is illuminated by the firelight, creating a dramatic effect against the dark sky.\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2693_6897_XingyuFan_ChinaMainland_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-800x600.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2693_6897_XingyuFan_ChinaMainland_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-320x240.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2693_6897_XingyuFan_ChinaMainland_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2693_6897_XingyuFan_ChinaMainland_Student_IntheBeginning_2025.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-776449\"\u003e© Xingyu Fan, Nanjing University of the Arts, China Mainland, Shortlist, Student Competition, Sony World Photography Awards 2025\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_776450\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-776450