rtlist-2695_6915_HonorataKornacka_Poland_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-800x533.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2695_6915_HonorataKornacka_Poland_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-320x213.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2695_6915_HonorataKornacka_Poland_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2695_6915_HonorataKornacka_Poland_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2695_6915_HonorataKornacka_Poland_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2695_6915_HonorataKornacka_Poland_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2695_6915_HonorataKornacka_Poland_Student_IntheBeginning_2025.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-776448\"\u003e© Honorata Kornacka, The Maria Grzegorzewska University, Poland, Shortlist, Student Competition, Sony World Photography Awards 2025\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_776451\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-776451\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2689_6877_ThapeloMahlangu_SouthAfrica_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-800x508.jpg\" alt=\"Four individuals in white robes stand in waist-deep water of a lake at dusk. One holds a cross, others place hands on a man\u0026#39;s head, performing a baptism. The background features tree silhouettes and a clear sky.\" width=\"800\" height=\"508\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2689_6877_ThapeloMahlangu_SouthAfrica_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-800x508.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2689_6877_ThapeloMahlangu_SouthAfrica_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-320x203.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2689_6877_ThapeloMahlangu_SouthAfrica_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-1536x974.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2689_6877_ThapeloMahlangu_SouthAfrica_Student_IntheBeginning_2025.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-776451\"\u003e© Thapelo Mahlangu, Stellenbosch Academy of Design and Photography, South Africa, Shortlist, Student Competition, Sony World Photography Awards 2025\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_776446\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-776446\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2699_6933_MontenezLowery_UnitedStates_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-800x547.jpg\" alt=\"On the left, a blurred, black-and-white photo of two people with braided hair, one adorned with a flower. On the right, a color photo of a tangled mass of what appears to be hair or yarn, with a small face peeking out.\" width=\"800\" height=\"547\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2699_6933_MontenezLowery_UnitedStates_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-800x547.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2699_6933_MontenezLowery_UnitedStates_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-320x219.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2699_6933_MontenezLowery_UnitedStates_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-1536x1050.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2699_6933_MontenezLowery_UnitedStates_Student_IntheBeginning_2025.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"cap