ates are also visible on the collage.\" width=\"534\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2701_6947_LounaPauly_France_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-534x800.jpg 534w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2701_6947_LounaPauly_France_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-213x320.jpg 213w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2701_6947_LounaPauly_France_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2701_6947_LounaPauly_France_Student_IntheBeginning_2025.jpg 1067w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 534px) 100vw, 534px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-776445\"\u003e© Louna Pauly, Ecole Nationale Supérieure Louis Lumière, France, Shortlist, Student Competition, Sony World Photography Awards 2025\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_776443\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-776443\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2705_6979_IlanaGrollman_UnitedStates_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A young person and an older person with glasses sit at a kitchen table, eyes closed. The kitchen is cluttered, with calendars and bags on the walls and various items on the counter. Sunlight brightens the room.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2705_6979_IlanaGrollman_UnitedStates_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2705_6979_IlanaGrollman_UnitedStates_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-320x213.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01/sony-world-photo-shortlist-2705_6979_IlanaGrollman_UnitedStates_Student_IntheBeginning_2025-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/01